      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely stunning, showroom-quality vehicle! This car is in mint condition, looking and driving exactly like it did the day it rolled off the lot. It has been meticulously maintained and cared for, offering a pristine interior and a flawless exterior that truly shines. If you're looking for perfection and a driving experience that feels brand new, this is the one for you!",
