    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It's the perfect reliable daily driver that still looks great pulling into any driveway. Everything runs smoothly, and it's totally ready for its next big adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home! \u2728",
      "price": 31500.0,
